data.title: Toronto Blue Jays Message Board
data.meta_description: On Twitter yesterday Barry Davis said he's only working half the Blue Jays games this season, splitting them with Hazel Mae.  Has Barry been demoted?  Maybe players complained and said they were sick of having to deal with him all the time.  I wonder if this was Barry's choice, or whether he was demoted by Rogers?  Last year I recall he worked every Jays game.
